<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Lienrum</author>
<hymn_number>239</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ni tum ngeilo Zion khawpi,
 Ngaia tauin sun tin nau bang ka kap;
 Tatsa te puon lopi silhin leng ui,
 Kei di'n mun a um dem zie gam achun?

[V2]
 Mu bang ka ngai, mu bang ka ngai,
 A mun lopi a hawihna cheng sangin;
 Lungsietpa Lal Krista mel deihum chu,
 Muh ka nuom lungkham sawl bang banna di'n.

[V3]
 2. A hawih zie gen senloh gam khu,
 Thisan in A hawng tai zalenna gam;
 Ka thagau zie gam ngei chu en zingin,
 Nuoi simlei hi pak bang tuoi ding ahi.

[V4]
 3. Lungdeih Hukdampa tuollenna,
 Tun theih loh ding ka lau ie Lal Isu;
 Thisan in ei silin, Thagau in ei puiin,
 Lal nunnem gam nuom mu bang ka ngai ie.</lyrics>
<title>Zion Khawpi Ngaihna</title>
</song>